casebody.data:
Rivka LIVNAT, Individually and as Personal Representative of the Estate of Ben-Yosef Livnat, et al., petitioners,
v.
PALESTINIAN AUTHORITY, aka The Palestinian Interim Self-Government Authority. No. 17-508. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2018. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied. Justice KAVANAUGH took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
